# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# vLLM DGX Spark Configuration — Nemotron-Cascade-2-30B-A3B
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Hybrid MoE (Mamba-2 + Transformer): 30B total / 3B active. Open weights.
# BF16 weight footprint ≈ 60 GB (fits single B200 110 GB comfortably).
# Strengths: IMO/IOI/ICPC gold-medal-level math & coding, LiveCodeBench 87.2,
#            AIME 2025 92.4, 262K context, thinking + instruct modes,
#            exceptional intelligence density (20× fewer params than frontier).
# Released: 2026-03-20
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Required for Multi-Node                                                 │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
WORKER_HOST="${WORKER_HOST:-}"
WORKER_IB_IP="${WORKER_IB_IP:-}"
WORKER_USER="${WORKER_USER:-$(whoami)}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Model Settings                                                          │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
MODEL="${MODEL:-nvidia/Nemotron-Cascade-2-30B-A3B}"

# Single B200 — 30B MoE fits BF16 without quantization
TENSOR_PARALLEL="${TENSOR_PARALLEL:-1}"

# ~60 GB weights leaves ~39 GB for KV + Mamba SSM cache at 0.90 util
GPU_MEMORY_UTIL="${GPU_MEMORY_UTIL:-0.90}"

# Supports 262K natively; default conservative for SSM cache headroom
MAX_MODEL_LEN="${MAX_MODEL_LEN:-262144}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Docker Settings                                                         │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
VLLM_IMAGE="${VLLM_IMAGE:-nvcr.io/nvidia/vllm:26.03-py3}"
HEAD_CONTAINER_NAME="${HEAD_CONTAINER_NAME:-ray-head}"
WORKER_CONTAINER_NAME="${WORKER_CONTAINER_NAME:-ray-worker}"
SHM_SIZE="${SHM_SIZE:-16g}"
RAY_VERSION="${RAY_VERSION:-2.54.0}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Network Settings                                                        │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
VLLM_PORT="${VLLM_PORT:-8000}"
RAY_DASHBOARD_PORT="${RAY_DASHBOARD_PORT:-8265}"
RAY_PORT="${RAY_PORT:-6385}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Storage Settings                                                        │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
HF_CACHE="${HF_CACHE:-/raid/hf-cache}"
WORKER_HF_CACHE="${WORKER_HF_CACHE:-${HF_CACHE}}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Authentication                                                          │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
HF_TOKEN="${HF_TOKEN:-}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ vLLM Options                                                            │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
# MoE model — enable expert parallelism
ENABLE_EXPERT_PARALLEL="${ENABLE_EXPERT_PARALLEL:-true}"

SWAP_SPACE="${SWAP_SPACE:-16}"

# Hybrid Mamba-2 architecture requires trust_remote_code
TRUST_REMOTE_CODE="${TRUST_REMOTE_CODE:-true}"

LOAD_FORMAT="${LOAD_FORMAT:-safetensors}"

# Nemotron reasoning parser; Mamba SSM cache must be float32;
# tool calling via qwen3_coder parser (per NVIDIA's recommendation)
EXTRA_ARGS="--reasoning-parser nano_v3 --trust-remote-code --enable-auto-tool-choice --tool-call-parser qwen3_coder"  # --reasoning-parser-plugin nano_v3_reasoning_parser.py

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ NCCL/InfiniBand Settings (auto-detected, override if needed)            │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
NCCL_DEBUG="${NCCL_DEBUG:-WARN}"
